      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/1/175/5861",
      "text": [
        " اَلدُّنْيَا قَالَ \"اَلَّذِي يَتْرُكُ حَلاَلَهَا مَخَافَةَ حِسَابِهِ وَ يَتْرُكُ حَرَامَهَا مَخَافَةَ عَذَابِهِ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.5861 - Abu Abdullah Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as), peace be upon him, was asked about the one who is ascetic in this world.\nImam (as) said: \"The one who abandons what is lawful out of fear of its reckoning and abandons what is unlawful out of fear of its punishment.\""
        ]
      }
    },
